=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] based o=
n the belief that =E2=80=9CThere is an opportunity for an industrial resear=
