ct/c61f093a-f673-402f-a341-a1dc045a06a9?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_Z=
lNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].=C2=A0
My hunch is that this is the beginning of a larger trend in which venture c=
