 return numbers I shared earlier, to support the industries they invest in =
in increasingly creative ways.=C2=A0
For firms with a long view, there=E2=80=99s an economic incentive to suppor=
t the kinds of things that have long, uncertain payoffs that doesn=E2=80=99=
t exist anywhere besides government and academia, both of which have become=
