The world gets accelerated research and knowledge in the bargain. Another f=
ree lunch. Yum.=C2=A0
Viva la VC=C2=A0
Venture capital is at a low point. According to Crunchbase, the $258 billio=
n venture capitalists invested in 2023 is the lowest amount they=E2=80=99ve=
 invested since 2017.=C2=A0
It=E2=80=99s not particularly popular, either. Certainly, VCs espousing pro=
