ine;">The Truth About Venture Capitalists</a></em><span> in 2007, NACUBO fo=
und that endowments allocated 3.5% of their assets to venture capital. In 2=
023, that number grew to 11.9%.&#160;</span></p><div class=3D"captioned-ima=
